name: The End
text: Give to the Gwendolyn Poole player. You cannot use speech bubbles from Gwenpool cards. Alter-Ego Action: Exhaust Gwendolyn Poole and discard Unbelievable Gwenpool → remove THE END from the game.

name: Rules of the Universe
text: Permanent. While there is no threat here, this scheme loses the [hazard] icon. Forced Interrupt: When you resolve an ability on a Gwenpool card, replace "_______" with the phrase from the speech bubble on Evil Gwenpool. [hazard]

name: Evil Gwenpool
text: Steady. Villainous. When Defeated: Shuffle Evil Gwenpool into the encounter deck. [star] Boost: Put Evil Gwenpool into play engaged with you. (Speech Bubble: "Gwenpool takes 1 damage.") (Gwenpool's nemesis minion.)

name: Break Reality
text: Incite 1. When Revealed: Search the encounter deck for Evil Gwenpool and reveal her. (Shuffle.) If Unbelievable Gwenpool is in play, she gains quickstrike. If Evil Gwenpool was already in play, add 2[per_hero] threat to Rules of the Universe.

name: "Future Me Scares Me"
text: Incite 0 (incite 1 instead, if this is a multiplayer game). Incite 1 (incite 2 instead, if this is an expert mode game). When Revealed: If Evil Gwenpool is in play, add 2 threat to Rules of the Universe and shuffle this card into the encounter deck.
